      "type": "text",
      "data": "<div class=\"wgt-ask accuse-response line mod-shadow\" id=\"wgt-ask\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\"><h1><span class=\"ask-title \">centos 7如何配置yum，在/etc/yum.repos下有6个.repo文件，怎么配置成</span></h1><div class=\"line mt-5 q-content\"><span class=\"con\">centos 7如何配置yum，在/etc/yum.repos下有6个.repo文件，怎么配置成一个文件，既包含光盘中的package又有镜像站，系统默认已安装了createrepo，越详细越好</span></div><div class=\"line f-aid ask-info ff-arial\" id=\"ask-info\"><span class=\"grid-r ask-time\"><ins class=\"share-area\"><div class=\"others-share\"><a title=\"\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"others-share-item weixin iknow-qb_share_icons\" data-type=\"weixin-click\"><span class=\"logo\"></span></a><a href=\"http://v.t.sina.com.cn/share/share.php?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzhidao.baidu.com%2Fquestion%2F490651343856915172%3Fsharesource%3Dweibo&amp;title=centos%207%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEyum%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%2Fetc%2Fyum.repos%E4%B8%8B%E6%9C%896%E4%B8%AA.repo%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%8C%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%88%90_%E7%99%BE%E5%BA%A6%E7%9F%A5%E9%81%93&amp;pic=https%3A%2F%2Fgss0.bdstatic.com%2F70cFsjip0QIZ8tyhnq%2Fimg%2Fiknow%2Fzhidaologo.png\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"others-share-item weibo iknow-qb_share_icons\" data-type=\"weibo-click\"><span class=\"logo\"></span></a><a href=\"http://connect.qq.com/widget/shareqq/index.html?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzhidao.baidu.com%2Fquestion%2F490651343856915172%3Fsharesource%3Dqq&amp;title=centos%207%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEyum%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%2Fetc%2Fyum.repos%E4%B8%8B%E6%9C%896%E4%B8%AA.repo%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%8C%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%88%90_%E7%99%BE%E5%BA%A6%E7%9F%A5%E9%81%93&amp;pics=https%3A%2F%2Fgss0.bdstatic.com%2F70cFsjip0QIZ8tyhnq%2Fimg%2Fiknow%2Fzhidaologo.png\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"others-share-item qq iknow-qb_share_icons\" data-type=\"qq-click\"><span class=\"logo\"></span></a><a href=\"http://sns.qzone.qq.com/cgi-bin/qzshare/cgi_qzshare_onekey?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzhidao.baidu.com%2Fquestion%2F490651343856915172%3Fsharesource%3Dqzone&amp;title=centos%207%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEyum%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%2Fetc%2Fyum.repos%E4%B8%8B%E6%9C%896%E4%B8%AA.repo%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%8C%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%88%90_%E7%99%BE%E5%BA%A6%E7%9F%A5%E9%81%93&amp;pics=https%3A%2F%2Fgss0.bdstatic.com%2F70cFsjip0QIZ8tyhnq%2Fimg%2Fiknow%2Fzhidaologo.png\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"others-share-item qzone iknow-qb_share_icons\" data-type=\"qzone-click\"><span class=\"logo\"></span></a></div></ins></span><a class=\" f-black\" rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zhidao.baidu.com/usercenter?uid=6b424069236f25705e796463\" target=\"_blank\">nodowns</a>&nbsp;<span id=\"v-times\" class=\"f-pipe\">|</span><span class=\"browse-times\">&nbsp;浏览 553 次</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"f-pipe\"></span>2015-10-22 22:22<ins class=\"accuse-area\"></ins></div></div><div class=\"hd line \" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\"><span class=\"grid-r f-aid pos-time answer-time\">2015-10-23 15:08&nbsp;</span><span class=\"iknow-qb_home_icons answer-type answer-best grid\"></span><span class=\"answer-title h2 grid\">最佳答案</span></div><div class=\"line info f-aid\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\"></div><pre id=\"best-content-2343341205\" class=\"best-text mb-10\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px;\">1、上传<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.baidu.com/s?wd=%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F&amp;tn=44039180_cpr&amp;fenlei=mv6quAkxTZn0IZRqIHckPjm4nH00T1YLP1bdnhmvrH6smWNWrjn40ZwV5Hcvrjm3rH6sPfKWUMw85HfYnjn4nH6sgvPsT6KdThsqpZwYTjCEQLGCpyw9Uz4Bmy-bIi4WUvYETgN-TLwGUv3EPjbsPWRkn1f1rjRvrHDdnHTz\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"baidu-highlight\">操作系统</a>镜像CentOS-6.5-x86_64-bin-DVD1.iso到/tmp下<br><br>2、建立目录并挂载镜像<br>mkdir /mnt/cdrom<br>mount -o loop /tmp/CentOS-6.5-x86_64-bin-DVD1.iso /mnt/cdrom/<br><br>3、设置本地repo<br>cat &lt;&lt;EOF &gt;/etc/yum.repos.d/loca-base.repo<br>[local-base]<br>name=loca-base<br>baseurl=<a href=\"file:///mnt/cdrom\">file:///mnt/cdrom</a> <br>gpgcheck=0<br>EOF<br>4、验证YUM源<br>yum repolist</pre>"
